{"tid":1019492,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[慎入] 《眼淚成詩》","createTime":"2019-02-13T03:40:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T03:41:55.000Z","uid":172990,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a61cb9cfc6f9613bb84e4fec7a0062d973083186","tid":1019492,"uid":172990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:40:31.000Z","msg":"《眼淚成詩》<br />\n<br />\n曲曲池邊路，春來少人行。<br />\n含水芙蓉葉，春去氣猶清。<br />\n夕嵐分彩翠，高樹藏鶯聲。<br />\n乍向風中看，花落更分明。<br />\n徘徊覺露冷，清宵月影橫。<br />\n泠泠砭肌發，疑是曉寒生。<br />\n一望可相見，一步如重城。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實講咁多 都係廢話 如果係我就skip左佢<br />\n最尾兩句先係重點<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n所愛隔山海<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n山海<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不可平</span>"},{"pid":"bce652571158c017ce382008048dad3f1ed66530","tid":1019492,"uid":172990,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:41:55.000Z","msg":"利申：好詩分享"}]}